OL,6,FUTV can reveal a senior police officer
OL,7,Fat the centre of a controversary over
OL,8,Fthe disappearance of a vacuum cleaner
OL,9,Ffrom a police station and claims the
OL,10,Ftried to blame the alleged theft on
OL,11,Fsubordinates has been able to retire
OL,12,Fbefore facing any disciplinary action.
