OL,3,CHandling of scandal dubbed
OL,4,C'hoovergate' branded 'a fiasco'
OL,6,FThe so-called Hoovergate scandal
OL,7,Ferupted in January 2021 when there
OL,8,Fwere tensions within the PSNI over an
OL,9,Falleged two-tier approach to
OL,10,Fdiscipline within the service.
OL,12,FIt's claimed the disappearance of the
OL,13,Fvacuum cleaner which was later
OL,14,Freturned was not properly investigated
OL,15,Ffirst time round to protect the top
OL,16,Fofficer.
