OL,6,FA second investigation was initiated,
OL,7,Fthis time by senior personnel at PSNI
OL,8,Fheadquarters. A file was sent to the
OL,9,FPPS for alleged theft ` a decision was
OL,10,Freached just a few months ago not to
OL,11,Fprosecute.
OL,13,FWe tried to contact the recently
OL,14,Fretired officer for comment but got no
OL,15,Fresponse.
OL,17,FOur latest Hoovergate revelation comes
OL,18,Fahead of proposed changes by the
OL,19,FDepartment of Justice to police
OL,20,Fconduct regulations.
